<% if (main_content_description) { %>
  <% if (main_content_description==="home" ) { %>
    <div class="Welcome_description">
      <div class="main_content">
        <h2 class="welcome_text">
          <%= welcome_text %>
        </h2>
        <div class="travel_description">
          <p>Travel Explorer is your ultimate guide to discovering the world's most breathtaking destinations. From
            iconic landmarks to hidden gems, our carefully curated guides help you plan unforgettable journeys across
            continents. Whether you're seeking adventure, culture, relaxation, or inspiration, Travel Explorer offers
            trusted tips, destination insights, and expert advice to make your travels smoother and more memorable. Let
            your next adventure begin here!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% } else if (main_content_description==="America" ) { %>
      <div class="Welcome_description">
        <div class="main_content_america">
          <h2 class="welcome_text">
            <%= welcome_text %>
          </h2>
          <div class="travel_description">
            <p>America spans vast landscapes and cultures, from the skyscrapers of New York City to the rainforests of
              Brazil and the pristine wilderness of Canada. North, Central, and South America together form a vibrant
              mosaic of history, nature, and modern marvels. Visitors can experience bustling cities, majestic
              mountains, tropical beaches, and ancient ruins, all while discovering the diverse heritage and spirit of
              each region. Whether you’re exploring iconic landmarks, immersing yourself in festivals, or embarking on
              epic road trips, the Americas offer journeys as bold and varied as their people.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <% } else if (main_content_description==="Europe" ) { %>
        <div class="Welcome_description">
          <div class="main_content_america">
            <h2 class="welcome_text">
              <%= welcome_text %>
            </h2>
            <div class="travel_description">
              <p>Europe is a continent rich in history, culture, and diversity. From the romantic streets of Paris to
                the ancient ruins of Rome and the sunny beaches of Spain, Europe offers a blend of old-world charm and
                modern sophistication. Travelers can explore medieval castles, art masterpieces, stunning landscapes,
                and culinary delights across many different countries — all within relatively short distances. Whether
                you're admiring Gothic cathedrals, hiking in the Alps, or tasting fresh pastries in a cozy café, Europe
                promises an unforgettable journey through time and tradition.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


        <% } else if (main_content_description==="Asia" ) { %>
          <div class="Welcome_description">
            <div class="main_content_america">
              <h2 class="welcome_text">
                <%= welcome_text %>
              </h2>
              <div class="travel_description">
                <p>Asia is the largest and most diverse continent on Earth, a fusion of ancient traditions and
                  futuristic cities. From the peaceful temples of Japan to the vibrant markets of Thailand and the
                  breathtaking beaches of Bali, Asia enchants travelers with its rich cultures, religions, landscapes,
                  and cuisines. Whether you're climbing sacred mountains, wandering through neon-lit metropolises, or
                  savoring spicy street food, Asia offers endless adventures and discoveries at every turn. It's a place
                  where centuries-old customs coexist with cutting-edge innovation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <% } else if (main_content_description==="Travel" ) { %>
            <div class="main_content_description">
              <h1 class="header_title">Destination: <%= travel.name %>
              </h1>
              <img src="<%= travel.image %>"alt="<%= travel.name %>"
                width="500px" height="auto"/>
                
                <p><strong>Country:</strong>
                  <%= travel.country %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong>
                  <%= travel.bestTimeToVisit %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Average Cost:</strong>
                  <%= travel.averageCost %>
                </p>

                

                <p><strong>Currency:</strong>
                  <%= travel.currency %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Language:</strong>
                  <%= travel.language %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>climate:</strong>
                  <%= travel.climate %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>food:</strong>
                  <%= travel.food %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>highlights:</strong>
                  <%= travel.highlights %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>attractions:</strong>
                  <%= travel.attractions %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>visa:</strong>
                  <%= travel.visa %>
                </p>
                <p><strong>Description:</strong>
                  <%= travel.description %>
                </p>


            </div>
            <% } %>
              <% } %>